│ `SimplifyDemandedUseBits`, which over-aggressively simplifies the operands of `fshl` based │
│ on the bits demanded by the `trunc` user. The logic fails to correctly account for the     │
│ interaction of bits from both operands of `fshl`, leading to an invalid transformation     │
│ that can produce `poison`.                                                                 │
